lines: Nda paila nendi enda, Leza ndikwele kujulu.
Leza kondi bweza njime, Mulusyomyo, munyik Ôeyo;
Cilawo ci inda eci, Leza ndikwele Kujulu.
Nsiyandi ku kala mumo, Muli kupengÔakuyowa;
Banji bala yanda muno, Ime ndayanda kujulu.
Nyanda kuya kuli Leza, Satani na ndi katazya;
Mbokuli lu syomo lwangu, Lwamvwa lwimbo lwa ku julu.
Ndayanda kuya kujulu, Kubona bulemu oko;
Pesi njaku pailisya, Limwi nkasike kujulu.
